content.rendered:
Directed by Anil Ravipudi.

Written by Anil Ravipudi.

Cast Sai Dharam Tej(Balu). Raashi Khanna(Bellam Sridevi). Rajendra Prasad(Balu’s father (as Rajendraprasad)). Ravi Kishan(Beeku). Sai Kumar(Narayana). Krishna Murali Posani(Musician Shivayya). Srinivasa Reddy(Musician Seenayya). Murali Mohan(Judge). Kabir Duhan Singh(Vikram Sarkar). Vennela Kishore(Kishore) . Mikail Gandhi(Rajan (as Mikhail Gandhi)). Giridhar(Venkatesh). Raghu Kumar Karumanchi(MLA’s henchman).Ravinder Kolishetty. Vineet Kumar(Patnaik). Jabardasth Naveen(Taxi driver). Prudhviraj(Tom). Satyam Rajesh(Rajesh). Shiju(Raja Rao). Sivannarayana(Sridevi’s uncle). Shruti Sodhi((Special appearance in a song)).Sudharshan

Language Telugu.

Producers Dil Raju. Sireesh.

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations.
